name: Advanced Laboratory in Human Biology
description: Building on their experience in 3rd-year labs, students participate in inquiry-based laboratory experiments in diverse areas of current human biology research. Open to students in any Human Biology program. Labs start in the first week of term. (Lab Materials Fee: $105)
prerequisites: 14 FCE complete, HMB310H1/ HMB311H1/ HMB312H1/ HMB314H1
